<p>
  Living in Japan is about following rules. (For comparison, living in
  Italy is about working around the rules). Today's rule is Garbage
  Disposal. In the households, one must distinguish among: "burnable",
  "non-burnable" (plastic), "resources" (PET/glass/paper).
</p>
